{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 2075, "title": "Fixup language around `NewType` in the spec", "body": "- Rather than stating that a call to `NewType()` returns a \"dummy function\" (which hasn't been true since Python 3.10), make the language more vague: describe it as returning a \"dummy callable object\" instead.\r\n- Add a cross-reference from the `NewType` section to a section elsewhere in the spec that discusses the interaction between `NewType` and `Protocol`\r\n\r\nFixes #2074", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "9d613b10bd1bfab483a9d0ccf82a3c6f6b1c4603", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "python/typing"}, "url": "https://github.com/python/typing/pull/2075", "createdAt": "2025-08-20T15:35:24Z", "mergedAt": "2025-08-20T18:13:25Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "python/typing"}, "sha": "9d613b10bd1bfab483a9d0ccf82a3c6f6b1c4603"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/python/typing/pull/2075.diff", "number": 2075, "created_at": "2025-08-20T15:35:24Z", "merged_at": "2025-08-20T18:13:25Z", "resolved_issues": [2074]}
{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 2098, "title": "Remove generic aliases", "body": "This PR closes #2083. I have made two changes to the [Typing Python Libraries](https://typing.python.org/en/latest/guides/libraries.html) documentation:\r\n\r\n- Use `list`, `dict`, `tuple` instead of `typing.List`, `typing.Dict`, `typing.Tuple` because the latter are [deprecated since Python 3.9](https://typing.python.org/en/latest/spec/historical.html#generics-in-standard-collections)\r\n- Use shorthand syntax for `typing.Union` and `typing.Optional` in accordance with the [Typing Best Practices](https://typing.python.org/en/latest/reference/best_practices.html#shorthand-syntax)", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "ecc212940ea9dd794604a5b5a68af38a95400d8f", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "python/typing"}, "url": "https://github.com/python/typing/pull/2098", "createdAt": "2025-10-11T10:28:59Z", "mergedAt": "2025-10-11T11:15:35Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "python/typing"}, "sha": "ecc212940ea9dd794604a5b5a68af38a95400d8f"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/python/typing/pull/2098.diff", "number": 2098, "created_at": "2025-10-11T10:28:59Z", "merged_at": "2025-10-11T11:15:35Z", "resolved_issues": [2083]}
