{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 2138, "title": "Use `pyproject.toml` instead of `setup.py`", "body": "The main motivation for this change is to migrate from the non-standard `setup.py` to the standard PEP 517 `setup.py`. The secondary motivation is to use a build backend that's easier to use and harder to get wrong than setuptools.\r\n\r\nModern build backends and much easier to use than setuptools, and will generally include `py.typed` and `.pyi` files automatically. This means we can remove the setuptools-specific documentation. We use `uv_build` for the stubs package example since it works out of the box with it.\r\n\r\npackaging.python.org has a tab system to show different build backends (https://packaging.python.org/en/latest/guides/writing-pyproject-toml/). Afaik typing.python.org doesn't, so we only show one build backend.\r\n\r\nFixes #2121", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "211b0cb5470e856f6093f7c3d688295f72f78bb6", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "python/typing"}, "url": "https://github.com/python/typing/pull/2138", "createdAt": "2025-12-18T11:27:20Z", "mergedAt": "2026-01-07T21:22:01Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "python/typing"}, "sha": "211b0cb5470e856f6093f7c3d688295f72f78bb6"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/python/typing/pull/2138.diff", "number": 2138, "created_at": "2025-12-18T11:27:20Z", "merged_at": "2026-01-07T21:22:01Z", "resolved_issues": [2121]}
{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 2146, "title": "Clarify that `tuple` should not be prohibited as an argument to `type`", "body": "Closes #2145\r\n\r\nThis spec change reconciles the typing spec and the conformance testsuite. `tuple` is an object of the `type` class, so it should be accepted as a value of `type`.", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "211b0cb5470e856f6093f7c3d688295f72f78bb6", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "python/typing"}, "url": "https://github.com/python/typing/pull/2146", "createdAt": "2026-01-06T22:14:20Z", "mergedAt": "2026-02-13T05:18:15Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "python/typing"}, "sha": "211b0cb5470e856f6093f7c3d688295f72f78bb6"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/python/typing/pull/2146.diff", "number": 2146, "created_at": "2026-01-06T22:14:20Z", "merged_at": "2026-02-13T05:18:15Z", "resolved_issues": [2145]}
